thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Kevin

author: Kevin
title: Kevin
text:
Sue was my contact when making the booking - so friendly and efficient I had nothing to worry about.
The car was exactly as described - in fact I thought I'd been upgraded, it was in such good condition.
Thankyou for making our family holiday to Nelson start perfectly straight from pick up outside the airport!
